{"tid":1693913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"A柱死角掰掰！美國14歲少女發明投影裝置獲科技創新競賽冠軍","createTime":"2019-11-05T01:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T01:55:20.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2009c1f15e341c580a0092a25686498a0d2007da","tid":1693913,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:07:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/P2BQUxIuqG8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FP2BQUxIuqG8&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=f67ab447\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/P2BQUxIuqG8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HxlNkIwqGb4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHxlNkIwqGb4&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=505cafbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HxlNkIwqGb4</a><br />\n<br />\n對轉彎車來說，A柱死角是最容易發生意外的原因，除了宣導駕駛在轉彎時要撇頭查看外，車廠在設計上也藉由更細的A柱或A柱側窗來減少視線死角的範圍。<br />\n <br />\n不過，現在有1名來自美國賓州的14歲少女Aliana Gassler，更透過簡單的投影裝置，讓車內駕駛能清楚看到A柱後方的車外情況，不僅有效解決A柱視線死角問題，也為她自己贏得Broadcom MASTERS（博通青少年科技創新大賽）冠軍！<br />\n <br />\n這套A柱投影系統是由攝影鏡頭、投影機與特殊反光材質組成，Gassler將鏡頭安裝在副駕座的A柱外側，並透過直播影像傳送到駕駛座上方的投影機，使畫面投影在副駕A柱上，讓A柱彷彿像是透明般的呈現車外景象。<br />\n <br />\n為了讓投影畫面更清楚，Gassler也在A柱包覆反光材質布料，因此即便是在車內的狹小空間，仍可將畫面清楚的投射至A柱，並且從副駕看過去則是一般黑色布料而已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4484/d4484436.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4484%2Fd4484436.jpg&h=025590a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這項發明使Gassler贏得Broadcom MASTERS青少年科技創新競賽冠軍，並獲得25,000美元獎金（約台幣76萬）。更重要的是，未來車廠也很可能透過類似想法解決A柱死角問題，降低意外事故發生。"},{"pid":"a33562c6344e430f4cd09b27d9ce18a7a67706a6","tid":1693913,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2fc874820dd66a58900e8f9f13a1621eb54ad7","tid":1693913,"uid":111425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:10:01.000Z","msg":"其實係人都做到 但諗到真係唔咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6292c1387616940acc14ade88efa81e4a6dfd45e","tid":1693913,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:12:08.000Z","msg":"唔係有sensor咩？"},{"pid":"7d9da19ce21516f5fd399ac6abbdb20afb21979b","tid":1693913,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:13:11.000Z","msg":"其實一早有專利 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6e65db82895a65f83d12472f01972e5dbb7c78","tid":1693913,"uid":72735,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3d2fc874820dd66a58900e8f9f13a1621eb54ad7","tid":1693913,"uid":111425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:10:01.000Z","msg":"其實係人都做到 但諗到真係唔咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:14:00.000Z","msg":"唔係調轉咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係人都諗到，做到就難"},{"pid":"a35ce7c9461721aeebbfee968cf3a6616f14e0b0","tid":1693913,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:27:55.000Z","msg":"A柱出面加2組鏡頭會唔會好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028d6a420cae832f77eca59dd97c5bf4ad47df53","tid":1693913,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db6e65db82895a65f83d12472f01972e5dbb7c78","tid":1693913,"uid":72735,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3d2fc874820dd66a58900e8f9f13a1621eb54ad7","tid":1693913,"uid":111425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:10:01.000Z","msg":"其實係人都做到